","msg":"<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1475000/1476889/concil_thumb_201608081_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1475000%2F1476889%2Fconcil_thumb_201608081_1024.jpg&h=1982da22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3084710b474e156eb12a746877a6dc3ea003f991","tid":2160871,"uid":41087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T09:21:29.000Z","msg":"留一年，之後成世選唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b5a367967b138d1327f36c946ca7fd7fe652887","tid":2160871,"uid":74763,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"31bf0ce87af4c3042e5a31fd6e2fe2c01407bcbd","tid":2160871,"uid":336186,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T08:53:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T09:32:35.000Z","msg":"單計今年已經有幾次會建制個邊唔齊人，泛民多人缺席而差幾票輸咗。<br />\n <br />\n如果你咁認同守住最後戰線，係咪應該迫咗呢班議員投票先？ 既然你咁認同盡做，咁大家盡做希望迫泛民佢地進步既時候 你應該支持埋一份。<br />\n<br />\n果期仲有班人不停講 泛民齊人投票對家都會睇住人數出，唔過半無用，借此宣傳下次選舉。咁留任點都唔過半係咪可以總辭得？同埋佢地真係你口中既票都唔投，你又點睇？<br />\n<br />\n對去留無乜大感覺，留任其實無乜所謂，錢都緊要既。但好似好多重大事件佢地都係眾籌，無乜邊次係自己夾錢，好似內會主席搵律師單野咁。呢兩年唔少人付出既錢都幾萬計，人工仲要無十皮，點解議員一次都無試過自己夾下錢每人出一皮？點解唔直接老實講養下面班細既？咁我都會敬重你照顧自己人既利益。<br />\n<br />\n唔好扮留底議會入面有反抗，特別係你地開會又唔齊人、國安法又過，連防疫果d 限聚令都唔駛問過立法會就推得。"},{"pid":"bd550e476bd43b86ca7ce07c70324e0a64660825","tid":2160871,"uid":73972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T09:41:34.000Z","msg":"咁市民意願呢"},{"pid":"d4fb1332cb67c47236644b9bc7684474d7a0c189","tid":2160871,"uid":336186,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T13:00:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fb32f1fb1b1bd34d684d9b8e167be58a4402a1f1","tid":2160871,"uid":49781,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d4fb1332cb67c47236644b9bc7684474d7a0c189","tid":2160871,"uid":336186,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T13:00:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T13:04:58.000Z","msg":"乜Q最後戰線<br />\n你哋都係答唔到我留任係點樣戰<br />\n奮鬥到底？前四年又唔見你講奮鬥到底？<br />\n真係bullshit<br />\n初選結果已經反映咗大多數人<br />\n都不滿你班泛民係議會表現<br />\n你繼續留任一個冇民意授權、非法延任嘅議會囉<br />\n他日香港真係完全冇民主，你班泛民都有份做成"},{"pid":"4ee55b2db7bcee4ae85eb61f7e95fe8882505892","tid":2160871,"uid":336186,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T14:34:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4363cd7e4ee0116cf799978b20067267fc0c6d42","tid":2160871,"uid":49781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ee55b2db7bcee4ae85eb61f7e95fe8882505892","tid":2160871,"uid":336186,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T14:34:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T14:36:38.000Z","msg":"你答咗我啲質疑先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"738bb3f0a91b76f76e0ff0187176a08c885c817b","tid":2160871,"uid":336186,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T14:38:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8ec4a31de782d4a7321f5a05e8b74311cd6abace","tid":2160871,"uid":49781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"738bb3f0a91b76f76e0ff0187176a08c885c817b","tid":2160871,"uid":336186,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4363cd7e4ee0116cf799978b20067267fc0c6d42","tid":2160871,"uid":49781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ee55b2db7bcee4ae85eb61f7e95fe8882505892","tid":2160871,"uid":336186,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T14:34:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T14:36:38.000Z","msg":"你答咗我啲質疑先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" c